name: Hombo-fahomboo
description: hombo-fahomboo, a mystique cat currently in Nias, North Sumatra, he is very enthusiastic about the pride of the Nias people "fahombo" (jumping stones). If you see him on Nias, he can jump right and left all day long, with a smile on his face. Don't forget he still likes to pee under a coconut tree.
